lead_paragraph: Moments after 21-year-old amateur Jared du Toit drained a dramatic 40-foot eagle putt to close out his third round at the Canadian Open at Saturday, the giant gallery around the 18th green serenaded their countryman with the national anthem.

headline.print_headline: Golf: Amateur Du Toit Has Fans Singing 'Oh Canada' at National Open
